1. preconditions and build
  create directory for ROS catkin workspace
  $ mkdir -p ros_catkin_ws/src

  ("${ros_comm}" is repository pj/BDK/ROS/ros_comm-kinetic-devel in gerrit)
  put "${ros_comm}" into ros_catkin_ws/src and then build
  $ cd ros_catkin_ws
  $ catkin_make               // Use '-j4' option at hikey machine.
  $ source devel/setup.bash

  Before running test, please run roscore first. Make sure that
  "roscore" for TCPROS/UDPROS and "ROS_UDS_EXT_ENABLE=on roscore"
  for UDSROS.

2. run
  $ cd src/"${ros_comm}"/test/test_perf_benchmark
  $ ./run_perf_test.sh test_loop_count subscirber_count transmission_type

  test_loop_count: the number of transmission
  subscirber_count: the number of subscriber
  transmission_type: choose in UDS and TCP_UDP
  note: The throughput size of this benchmark is 256B, 4KB, 256KB, 2MB and 8MB.

